---

<h2>7. Image Optimization</h2>

<p>
Images should:
</p>

<ul>
<li>Have descriptive filenames</li>
<li>Include alt text</li>
<li>Be compressed for speed</li>
</ul>

---

<h2>8. URL Structure</h2>

<p>
Your URLs should be:
</p>

<ul>
<li>Short</li>
<li>Keyword-rich</li>
<li>Readable</li>
</ul>

<p>
Example:
</p>

<p>
<strong>/blog/on-page-seo-checklist-2026.html</strong>
</p>

---

<h2>9. Page Speed Optimization</h2>

<p>
Fast websites rank higher.
</p>

<p>
Improve speed by:
</p>

<ul>
<li>Compressing images</li>
<li>Reducing code</li>
<li>Using caching</li>
</ul>

---

<h2>10. Mobile Optimization</h2>

<p>
Most users are on mobile.
</p>

<p>
Your site must:
</p>

<ul>
<li>Be responsive</li>
<li>Load fast</li>
<li>Be easy to navigate</li>
</ul>

